There was one other sighting in Winnipeg on or around July 14th 2012
divs: Sighting DetailsObserved the objects from the back yard... Objects appeared out of the north and proceeded south west, and then disappeared. First thought they were flare like, but they stayed lit abd bright as they passed over. Objects were in groups of 2-3 and all on the same path south west. They all travelled at a similar speed... Very strange and odd....
